@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tkyenm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos(0.66))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.35)) * v2)
    tmp = v1
    tmp = 0.25
    v1 = (0.33 + wp.exp(tmp))
    v1 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v0 = (tmp - (wp.abs(v2 + 0.06) + v1))
    data[tid] = v0
